{"tid":373210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber澳門重開 推三天義載","createTime":"2017-08-25T00:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T01:24:35.000Z","uid":25556,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"259a3bc28f9943bddd3d20838af2a107d462b308","tid":373210,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:50:34.000Z","msg":"颱風「天鴿」昨日橫掃澳門，原本已撤出澳門的Uber表示，澳門經歷嚴重風災，部份交通工具受破壞，故決定今天晚上9時重開Uber App，在未來的三天，舉行義載，方便民眾出行。<br />\n<br />\nUber 發言人表示，由於這次是義務提供服務，並不會收取酬，但提醒市民留給有急需的市民預約叫車。集團澳門總經理盧綺雯表示，颱風天鴿肆虐澳門，希望在艱難時間，為澳門出一分力，並感激司機夥伴的支持，在短時間內響應義載。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1503582031721&amp;issue=20170824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1503582031721%26issue%3D20170824&d=L4AMZ6LbyX1Qs6BI5eXwoRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ab1f30f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1503582031721&amp;issue=20170824</a><br />\n<br />\n的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7810f724df21ddef11ba3b69f28a76f6ce603f4b","tid":373210,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"得幾架車出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bf18b35ce4abee81856141692f24a1e26715a1","tid":373210,"uid":25556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T01:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得幾架車出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼唔係趁火打劫"},{"pid":"5db3d042b945a3cc4d0da6b473d5e9de7ba321e9","tid":373210,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T01:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得幾架車出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登仔真係難服侍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff0f2df2d4a9d122abe9dbef044b90e10d1dead","tid":373210,"uid":55913,"li